  "root_text": {
    "an6.120-139:0.1": "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6.120–139 ",
    "an6.120-139:0.2": "12. Sāmaññavagga ",
    "an6.120-139:0.3": "Bhallikādisutta ",
    "an6.120-139:1.1": "“Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhalliko gahapati …pe… ",
    "an6.120-139:1.2": "sudatto gahapati anāthapiṇḍiko … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.3": "citto gahapati macchikāsaṇḍiko … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.4": "hatthako āḷavako … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.5": "mahānāmo sakko … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.6": "uggo gahapati vesāliko … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.7": "uggato gahapati … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.8": "sūrambaṭṭho … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.9": "jīvako komārabhacco … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.10": "nakulapitā gahapati … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.11": "tavakaṇṇiko gahapati … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.12": "pūraṇo gahapati … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.13": "isidatto gahapati … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.14": "sandhāno gahapati … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.15": "vicayo gahapati … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.16": "vijayamāhiko gahapati … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.17": "meṇḍako gahapati … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.18": "vāseṭṭho upāsako … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.19": "ariṭṭho upāsako … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.20": "sāraggo upāsako tathāgate niṭṭhaṅgato amataddaso amataṁ sacchikatvā iriyati. ",
    "an6.120-139:1.21": "Katamehi chahi? ",
    "an6.120-139:1.22": "Buddhe aveccappasādena, dhamme aveccappasādena, saṅghe aveccappasādena, ariyena sīlena, ariyena ñāṇena, ariyāya vimuttiyā. ",
    "an6.120-139:1.23": "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato sāraggo upāsako tathāgate niṭṭhaṅgato amataddaso amataṁ sacchikatvā iriyatī”ti. ",
    "an6.120-139:1.24": "Tevīsatimaṁ. ",
    "an6.120-139:1.25": "Sāmaññavaggo dvādasamo. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "an6.120-139:0.1": "Numbered Discourses 6.120–139 ",
    "an6.120-139:0.2": "12. The Ascetic Life ",
    "an6.120-139:0.3": "About Bhallika, Etc. ",
    "an6.120-139:1.1": "“Mendicants, having six qualities the householders Bhallika … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.2": "Sudatta Anāthapiṇḍika … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.3": "Citta of Macchikāsaṇḍa … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.4": "Hatthaka of Āḷavī … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.5": "Mahānāma the Sakyan … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.6": "Ugga of Vesālī … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.7": "Uggata … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.8": "Sūrambaṭṭha … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.9": "Jīvaka Komārabhacca … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.10": "Nakula’s father … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.11": "Tavakaṇṇika … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.12": "Pūraṇa … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.13": "Isidatta … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.14": "Sandhāna … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.15": "Vijaya … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.16": "Vijayamāhita … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.17": "Meṇḍaka … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.18": "the lay followers Vāseṭṭha … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.19": "Ariṭṭha … ",
    "an6.120-139:1.20": "and Sāragga are certain about the Realized One, see freedom from death and live having realized freedom from death. ",
    "an6.120-139:1.21": "What six? ",
    "an6.120-139:1.22": "Experiential confidence in the Buddha, the teaching, and the Saṅgha, and noble ethics, knowledge, and freedom. ",
    "an6.120-139:1.23": "Having these six qualities the lay follower Sāragga is certain about the Realized One, sees freedom from death and lives having realized freedom from death.” ",
    "an6.120-139:1.24": ""
  },
